\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1  The relationship the spectral optical depth with the spectral absorbance can be denoted with following equation : \par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qc\f1\fs24\'f4\sub\f0 v\nosupersub  = A\sub v\nosupersub ln10\par
