\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1\fs20  Thus, with regard to the optical depth \f1\'f4\f0\fs24  \fs20 and absorbance A, in comparable condition with above one, the equations also can be defined\par
\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1\qc\f1\fs24\'f4\f0  = l \f1\'d3\sub\f0 i=1\super N\nosupersub  \f1\'f3\sub\f0 i\nosupersub n\sub i\par
